            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1259-v2-Step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es] </strong>into quarters, scoop out the seeds with a spoon and discard</p><p>Dice the<strong> deseeded tomato</strong> finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1259.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
