            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped tomato</strong> and <strong>parsley</strong> to a bowl with the<strong> garlic & shallot oil </strong>(reserve the pan)</p><p>Squeeze in the juice of <strong>half</strong> your<strong> lemon[s] </strong>and season with a generous pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> tomato relish</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1259-v2-Step-5-x200.jpg",
