            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a high heat with a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Pat your <strong>cod fillet[s]</strong> dry with kitchen paper and season generously with <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
