    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add the <strong>cod</strong> to the pan with a knob of<strong> butter</strong> and cook for 4-5 min on each side or until cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p><p>Add a large knob of<strong> butter</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>to the pot with the drained potatoes, and crush them lightly with a fork</p>",
